videos.description: Ryan Wolpin gets the quick toss on the outside and follows his blockers for a 1-yard touchdown to go up early over Oregon.
videos.headline: Interesting blocking technique helps Boise State score first

videos.description: Brett Rypien throws it downfield to a wide-open Sean Modster who fights for extra yards for a gain of 50.
videos.headline: Boise State gains 50 on wide-open pitch-and-catch

videos.description: Brett Rypien throws an errant pass in the end zone and Oregon's Arrion Springs makes an incredible one-handed catch for the interception.
videos.headline: Ducks deny Broncos with 1-handed INT in end zone

videos.description: Tony Brooks-James coughs up the ball after a hit by Leighton Vander Esch and the Broncos are there for the recovery.
videos.headline: Ducks give it right back after fumble

videos.description: Cedrick Wilson gets a pass across the middle and finds daylight ahead of him for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Broncos capitalize off fumble with passing TD

videos.description: Justin Herbert underthrows his receiver and Jordan Happle is there for the interception and the Broncos' third takeaway of the first half.
videos.headline: Boise State takes it away for the 3rd time in the 1st half

videos.description: Justin Herbert misfires on his throw to the outside and Kekaula Kaniho returns the interception 53 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Broncos' 3rd INT goes for a pick-6

videos.description: Boise State tries their famed Statue of Liberty play inside the red zone, but the Broncos fumble the hand-off and Troy Dye returns it 86 yards for an Oregon TD.
videos.headline: Boise State's Statue of Liberty play goes all wrong

videos.description: Tyree Robinson intercepts Brett Rypien's pass on the goal line and hustles 100 yards down the sideline for back-to-back defensive touchdowns for Oregon.
videos.headline: 100-yard pick-6 gets Ducks within 10

videos.description: Oregon head coach Mario Cristobal wants to get the offense back on track and settle down QB Justin Herbert, but wants the defense to keep up their solid production.
videos.headline: Oregon's Cristobal: Defense has found a way to stand up'

videos.description: Boise State head coach Bryan Harsin wants his team to take the second half one play at a time and to act as if the score is 0-0.
videos.headline: Boise State's Harsin: 'One play at a time'

videos.description: Brett Rypien connects with Cedrick Wilson, who stops on a dime to dive for a 30-yard gain.
videos.headline: Wilson makes another great catch for big Boise gain

videos.description: Brett Rypien tosses it to Alec Dhaenens who bounces off of a defender and dives over the pylon for the 13-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Boise State opens up 2nd half with passing TD

videos.description: Justin Herbert throws a 24-yard strike to Brenden Schooler in the corner of the end zone as the Ducks climb back to within 10.
videos.headline: Herbert throws a perfect ball for Oregon TD

videos.description: The Broncos are so in sync on offense, they choreograph blockers to help Ryan Wolpin get in for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Boise State's choreographed offense leads to TD

videos.description: Justin Herbert slings a pass to the back of the end zone for Jaylon Redd who makes the grab for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Ducks hang around after 4th-down TD

videos.description: Boise State head coach Bryan Harsin took an ice bath and said that this team is deserving of winning the Las Vegas Bowl.
videos.headline: Boise State's Harsin: 'There's a great vibe about this group'

videos.description: Cedric Wilson finishes with 10 catches, 221 yards and a touchdown as the Broncos beat Oregon in the Las Vegas Bowl.
videos.headline: Cedric Wilson wins MVP of Las Vegas Bowl

videos.description: Boise State head coach Bryan Harsin says winning the Las Vegas Bowl is what being a Bronco is all about.
videos.headline: Coach Harsin: 'This group right here is special'

videos.description: Cedric Wilson and Leighton Vander Esch call out to their teammates in jubilation saying this is a special team.
videos.headline: Cedric Wilson: 'I went out and played for my brothers'

videos.description: Boise State knocks off Oregon in Vegas 38-28 to capture its fourth Las Vegas Bowl title.
videos.headline: Boise State hoists the Las Vegas Bowl trophy

videos.description: Rece Davis and Kirk Herbstreit break down why Boise State performed so well and what these two programs have to offer for next year.
videos.headline: Boise State takes down Oregon in the Las Vegas Bowl

videos.description: Brett Rypien throws for 362 yards and two touchdowns and Ryan Wolpin runs for 71 yards and two scores as Boise State defeats Oregon 38-28.
videos.headline: Boise State wins Las Vegas Bowl
